z (Pachuca) y Edson Álvarez (West Ham United).</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mediocampistas</strong>: Luis Romo (Cruz Azul), Obed Vargas (Seattle Sounders), Marcel Ruíz (Toluca), Carlos Rodríguez (Cruz Azul), Andrés Guardado (León), Sebastián Córdova (Tigres) y Orbelin Pineda (AEK Atenas).</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><strong>Delanteros</strong>: Diego Lainez (Tigres), Roberto Alvarado (Chivas), Ozziel Herrera (Tigres), Germán Berterame (Monterrey), César Huerta (Pumas), Alexis Vega (Toluca), Guillermo Martínez (Pumas), Raúl Jiménez (Fulham) y Henry Martín (América).</p>","related_article":[{"identifier":"vela-y-ochoa-201clas-puertas-abiertas201d-para-regresar-al-tri-201cvasco201d-aguirre-6044.html","uuid":"30addbb30ee04d8b8e3280fd64f4464d"},{"identifier":"aquel-que-no-entienda-la-filosofia-del-tri-se-puede-ir-a-casa-aguirre-1785.html","uuid":"8732b37806cd4e73955f259ad7da59b4"},{"identifier":"en-el-regreso-de-javier-aguirre-el-tri-golea-a-nueva-zelanda-9243.html","uuid":"be1c40f0bf3a4dbbb31e41cac6c46400"}],"media_images":{"content_images":[{"descripcion":"Foto del perfil de X de la Selección Nacional","author":"","dirbucket":"jornadaimg/ochoa-jimenez-y-guardado-regresan-al-tricolor-para-la-fecha-fifa-3863/ochoa-jimenez-y-guardado-regresan-al-tricolor-para-la-fecha-fifa-3863html-convocatoriajpg-3601html-4853330a-58ae-4c22-a371-9b8d263fe46f.jpg","displayphoto":"https://www.jornada.com.mx/ndjsimg/images/jornada/jornadaimg/ochoa-jimenez-y-guardado-regresan-al-tricolor-para-la-fecha-fifa-3863/ochoa-jimenez-y-guardado-regresan-al-tricolor-para-la-fecha-fifa-3863html-convocatoriajpg-3601html-4853330a-58ae-4c22-a371-9b8d263fe46f.jpg"}]},"media_videos":{"content_videos":[]},"word_count":302,"url":"https://www.jornada.com.mx/noticia/2024/09/30/deportes/ochoa-jimenez-y-guardado-regresan-al-tricolor-para-la-fecha-fifa-3863","location":"cdmx","style_headline":"default","extra_data":{}}}},{"identifier":"liga-mx-lament